Class Runway

  • java.lang.Object
    • Runway

  • public class Runway
extends java.lang.Object
    Runway class that holds a list of planes specified to specific runway. User will enter new and existing to planes to list in the runway class
    Author:
    Brian Mendoza, Merry DeGaga
